    <string name="help_sectionlist_text">I konei ka taea e koe te whakaingoa, te whakaahua me te whakatika i nga korero o to Wātū.\n\nWHAKATOKANGA\nHei whakarite ano i nga taonga, pehia roa i runga i tetahi mea me te\ntoia ki tona turanga hou.\n\nTE MUMU\nHei muku i tetahi mea, nukuhia ki te taha matau.\n\nEDITA\nHei whakatika i tetahi waahanga, pa noa kia kotahi.\n\nTāpiri\nHei taapiri i tetahi waahanga hou, pehia te paatene +.</string>
